{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pullrequests/94/comments/16359834.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pull-requests/94/_/diff#comment-16359834"}}, "parent": {"id": 16351294, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pullrequests/94/comments/16351294.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pull-requests/94/_/diff#comment-16351294"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 94, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pullrequests/94.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pull-requests/94"}}, "title": "Fix coverity issues"}, "content": {"raw": "One catch about using raw opaque pointers is that we have to make sure they're deleted in the destructor after all other members. Recently we found a [problem](https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/commits/62aae1c1e2eb) in Gazebo where a publisher pointer was being cleaned up after the raw pointer and that caused occasional crashes.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>One catch about using raw opaque pointers is that we have to make sure they're deleted in the destructor after all other members. Recently we found a <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/commits/62aae1c1e2eb\" rel=\"nofollow\">problem</a> in Gazebo where a publisher pointer was being cleaned up after the raw pointer and that caused occasional crashes.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2016-03-28T17:28:31.424431+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": "2016-03-28T17:29:29.038519+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 16359834}